ent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AyMjO2l10Y5xUm2Z7WeUHq4&oh=00_AYDfsacDuQH9tEK8ZtbV8s28TW0SYQ4gm4rJdijbFbf5pQ&oe=66EACCFE"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "cover.png", "id": "1450189568960094", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75458102_1450189572293427_321153024598500436_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5qCnDKVsxeEQ7kNvgEvErbb&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AyMjO2l10Y5xUm2Z7WeUHq4&oh=00_AYA_F3vTqq-BMHyk8-iT7WWCMScbz_LQFW84y_ElXbc4SA&oe=66EACD7B"}, "display_name": "Strike Master", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Strike Master: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Strike Master,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters a realm of immersive virtual reality. Get ready to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Strike Master\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport.\nGame Overview\n\n\"Strike Master\" is a cutting-edge VR game that redefines the bowling experience by placing players in a vibrant cosmic arena. The game challenges your precision, skill, and timing as you aim to score points by knocking down pins in various celestial-themed lanes. Each game session offers a unique adventure, filled with stunning visuals and dynamic gameplay.", "short_description": "Strike Master: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Strike Master,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters a realm of immersive virtual reality. Get ready to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Strike Master\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/strike-